Package com.informatics.lehigh.cardboardarlibrary

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GLRenderer
    Basic interface describing a class that sets up, updates, and executes rendering of an object for the Google Cardboard using OpenGL.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CameraTextureRenderer
    Renderer for drawing the camera feed on a SurfaceTexture (GL_TEXTURE_EXTERNAL_OES) to a normal Texture2D.
    Cube
    Cube consisting of 6 different markers.
    CubeConfiguration
    Configuration of a Cube with positions of marker IDs.
    CubeDetector
    Detector for finding marker Cube objects in an image frame.
    CVUtil
    Contains static utility methods for various OpenCV operations.
    GarActivity
    The main activity of AR applications should extend this activity.
    GarUtil
    Utility class for various OpenGL and GAR operations.
    StereoScreenRenderer
    Renderer that draws a screen in front of the viewer textured with the combination of two textures: the physical device camera view, and the augmented objects.
